## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible motivations for entrepreneurship. Individual motivations can be highly personal and varied, and this report focuses on the most commonly cited reasons. Additionally, the sources used are primarily from Western perspectives, which may not fully represent global entrepreneurial motivations.

